column5: Lewski the snowman with a moustache full of snow  Where's your corncob pipe, button nose and two eyes made out of coal ???  Just kidding Lew...I was covered just as bad yesterday...a bit better with light winds today...
That pic was taken in Rio??
That picture is priceless  *right click - save*  Joey
It just doesn't matter what his pics look like .............he still makes me giggle every time I see one of his pics with those expressions of just wanting to crack a smile.  Regards, Sam
How heavy was the ice on you mustache Lew.Could you talk with all that weight
I know who he is now...  You ever seen that old Bugs Bunny cartoon where he's in the Yukon ?  Old Bugs has some issues with a guy named "Black Jack Shellac" = Lew   Hookset.
